<p>LOTI, Pierre. <em>Un p&egrave;lerin d&rsquo;Angkor</em>. CreateSpace, 2015. 78 pages.</p>

<p>BIZOT, Fran&ccedil;ois. <em>Le portail.</em> Gallimard, 2002 [Folio]. 439 pages.</p>

<p>MALRAUX, Andr&eacute;. <em><a href="http://www.amazon.fr/gp/product/2253010359/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=amicamazon-21&amp;camp=1642&amp;creative=6746&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;creativeASIN=2253010359&amp;linkId=9661acf5703695ef86c9b0928eec3748" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">La voie royale</a>.</em> Le Livre de Poche, 1976 [Litt&eacute;rature &amp; Documents]. 192 pages.</p>

