<p>PAVIE, Auguste.&nbsp;<em><a href="https://www.amazon.fr/gp/product/2738435203/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=amicamazon-21&amp;camp=1642&amp;creative=6746&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;creativeASIN=2738435203&amp;linkId=f3b6d2a4006ad13b0cdb0422bb140f9f" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Au Royaume du million d&rsquo;&eacute;l&eacute;phants</a></em>.&nbsp;Editions L&#39;Harmattan, 2000 [M&eacute;moires asiatiques].&nbsp;380 pages.</p>

<p>PHOLSENA, Vatthana.&nbsp;<em><a href="https://www.amazon.fr/Laos-Un-pays-en-mutation/dp/2701154081/ref=sr_1_10?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1370425387&amp;sr=1-10&amp;keywords=laos" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Un pays en mutation</a></em>.&nbsp;Belin, 2011 [Asie plurielle].&nbsp;192 pages.</p>

