	<li>C&rsquo;est trop cher&nbsp;: Zay gyi deh</li>
	<li>H&ocirc;tel&nbsp;: Hawtal</li>
	<li>Bon app&eacute;tit&nbsp;: Kaung kaung sar gya bar</li>
	<li>un, deux, trois, quatre, cinq, six, sept, huit, neuf, dix&nbsp;: tit / nit / thone / lay / ngar / chauk / khone / shit / koe / tasae</li>
